    "description": "Dream Loop is a first person exploration and puzzle experience, with an innovative music-based twist. Immerse yourself in an atmospheric dreamscape, capturing sounds from the environment to mix together to create looping tracks. What sounds mesh and what sounds clash is up to you to discover, as you create your next great album, track by track!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/6ecfec6fdf3a53dfbc2cac46645065c3.avif?t=1643088883\" width=600 height=316 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CENTER YOURSELF</strong></h2>…in a deeply emotional audio experience with immersive, meditative gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/2fd2a208a4f761f69071156ee1218a7b.poster.avif?t=1643088883\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/2fd2a208a4f761f69071156ee1218a7b.webm?t=1643088883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/2fd2a208a4f761f69071156ee1218a7b.mp4?t=1643088883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></h2>…stunningly beautiful visuals and mind bending dreamscapes that mimic the experience of lucid dreaming. Breathtaking locations featuring contemporary art and architecture, high fashion and vivid landscapes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/7a3ae13acc60f1a07597e8a11e9c46f1.poster.avif?t=1643088883\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/7a3ae13acc60f1a07597e8a11e9c46f1.webm?t=1643088883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/7a3ae13acc60f1a07597e8a11e9c46f1.mp4?t=1643088883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOLVE</strong></h2>…innovative “music looping” puzzles. Mix and match loops created from the sounds in the environment. Find the sounds that belong together, &amp; be rewarded with lush, fresh original tracks, accompanied by outlandish visuals.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/74e95c9b484c8d5b74ff12b0e658fdbe.poster.avif?t=1643088883\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/74e95c9b484c8d5b74ff12b0e658fdbe.webm?t=1643088883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/74e95c9b484c8d5b74ff12b0e658fdbe.mp4?t=1643088883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNCOVER</strong></h2>…a tragic love story from beyond the grave – and find your inspiration in the most unlikely of places. With vintage tape recorder in hand, set out on an atmospheric adventure to create your next album, recording the sounds from your surreal environment to create each track.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/50fff0c4ef760ed06fe518004bae9cb4.avif?t=1643088883\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TURN UP YOUR HEADPHONES</strong></h2>…and drop out. Completely original soundtrack and exquisitely crafted sound design create an immersive and deeply emotional audio experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800670/extras/5f5aec50142e738577fd9ac0192c53c8.avif?t=1643088883\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
